            <h1 class="hero-h1 mt-6 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-[0.10em] uppercase leading-[1.02]">
              Privacy & Civil Liberties
            </h1>

            <p class="hero-lead mt-8 text-[16px] md:text-[18px] leading-relaxed text-slateblue measure">
              This framework defines NADIR’s data boundaries for policy-scoped evidentiary capture. NADIR is designed to support institutional verification without default exposure of proprietary IP, unnecessary personal data, or secondary-use surveillance.
            </p>

